rDiff version 0.3 (14 January, 2013)
---------------------------------------

The new veriosn of rDiff contains now two new tests, rDiff.parametric and
rDiff nonparametric. The code has been completly rewritten and is now considerably
faster and more stable.

rDiff version 0.1 (September, 2011)
----------------------------------------

This is the first release of rDiff, which is a tool for differential
expression testing of RNA-Seq data.
Please also visit http://fml.mpg.de/raetsch/suppl/rdiff for more
information about this software.
